{"tid":2092210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"團體促公開武力指引","createTime":"2020-07-03T06:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T07:37:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"daff22a3fedcfa4cf6f604a428fe65f5d2508922","tid":2092210,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/2Z765OZN353BZ5RQ7SKLCPXLSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2F2Z765OZN353BZ5RQ7SKLCPXLSM%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=aae051f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2F2Z765OZN353BZ5RQ7SKLCPXLSM%2F&h=8d94498c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/2Z765OZN353BZ5RQ7SKLCPXLSM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n團體促公開武力指引<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f7LsfljT6KXuKPxzk0TXff3a5oQ=/190x152/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PXKBL24G2Q5JWA6PSAIHTUUZCY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff7LsfljT6KXuKPxzk0TXff3a5oQ%3D%2F190x152%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPXKBL24G2Q5JWA6PSAIHTUUZCY.gif&h=07b01fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網媒Flash Media攝記迎面中水炮，之後彈飛兩米倒地。有線電視畫面<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方斥資1,660萬元購入三輛俗稱水炮車的「人群管理特別用途車」，去年向立法會議員及傳媒示範操作，但拒絕披露相關武力指引，只稱主要射向目標下肢，更聲稱殺傷力「好低」。有人權組織要求警方盡快公開水炮車的武力指引，否則公眾難以監察警方執法。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傳媒隨時中招 譚耀宗：明眼人識分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n200磅假人被噴飛8米<br />\n<br />\n據<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n如射程50米時每分鐘可射水1,200公升；車頭有個防衞水炮，射程則為40米。去年警方向議員及傳媒示範，將水炮車水壓調至最高程度，重逾200磅的假人在20至30米距離內被射至退後8米，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察成員沈偉男稱，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n否則公眾及傳媒難以監察其使用武力是否合乎指引。<br />\n<br />\n議員毛孟靜去年有份參觀警方示範，她指當日警方聲稱水炮車殺傷力好低，只會用作驅散人群，「當時我已經質疑會唔會咁輕威力」。對於警方迄未披露水炮車的執行細節，包括如何判斷發射威力的程度等，毛表示會在立法會跟進。"},{"pid":"911d701b4c164cb6fad467abb2e528f707b34d18","tid":2092210,"uid":82359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"都無，點公開？"},{"pid":"9741b1d10a5fbd62c16033099659aeb8ee79daa2","tid":2092210,"uid":238844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"911d701b4c164cb6fad467abb2e528f707b34d18","tid":2092210,"uid":82359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"都無，點公開？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T07:37:58.000Z","msg":"同我反應一L樣"}]}